    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Summarize long emails with Google Drive and Discord with instant alerts\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nSummarize long emails with Google Drive and Discord with instant alerts. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual auto-reply is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Keep Valid Tickets → Detect Sentiment → Escalate Negative — Discord → Collect All Outcomes → Tag Pipeline Metadata → Align Field Names → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating auto-reply in customer support\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Improves response time\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Discord webhook URL; Google OAuth2 / service account; Groq API key.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "619c3453-0bf9-c79e-6ef8-b4758fa174cc",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
